#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/perseids.tsx:120
msgid "A comfortable chair or blanket is more useful than a telescope, as meteors can appear anywhere overhead."
msgstr "Kursi yang nyaman atau selimut lebih berguna daripada teleskop, karena meteor bisa muncul di mana saja di atas kepala."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/autumn-equinox.tsx:110
msgid "A time of turning"
msgstr "Saat peralihan"

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/total-lunar-eclipse.tsx:42
msgid "A total lunar eclipse occurs when the Earth moves directly between the Sun and the Moon, fully shading the lunar surface."
msgstr "Gerhana Bulan total terjadi ketika Bumi bergerak tepat di antara Matahari dan Bulan, sehingga permukaan Bulan tertutupi sepenuhnya."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/total-solar-eclipse.tsx:33
msgid "A total solar eclipse occurs when the Moon moves directly in front of the Sun, briefly transforming daylight into twilight."
msgstr "Gerhana Matahari total terjadi ketika Bulan bergerak tepat di depan Matahari, sejenak mengubah siang menjadi senja."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/summer-solstice.tsx:119
msgid "Above the Arctic Circle, the sun doesn't set at all — it traces a low circle along the horizon and starts climbing again. This is the midnight sun, and it lasts for weeks."
msgstr "Di atas Lingkaran Arktik, matahari tidak terbenam sama sekali — ia membentuk lingkaran rendah di sepanjang cakrawala dan mulai naik kembali. Inilah matahari tengah malam, dan ia berlangsung selama berminggu-minggu."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/hanukkah.tsx:90
msgid "According to tradition, a small supply of oil, meant for one day, lasted eight."
msgstr "Menurut tradisi, persediaan minyak kecil yang seharusnya cukup untuk satu hari bertahan selama delapan hari."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/christmas.tsx:71
msgid "Across centuries and cultures, distinctive local practices emerged — from midnight services and carolling to bustling festive markets and public celebrations."
msgstr "Selama berabad-abad dan lintas budaya, praktik lokal yang khas berkembang — dari misa tengah malam dan nyanyian Natal hingga pasar meriah dan perayaan publik."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/autumn-equinox.tsx:97
msgid "Across many ancient cultures, this point in the year was closely tied to harvest celebrations, gratitude, and preparation for winter."
msgstr "Dalam banyak budaya kuno, titik ini dalam setahun terkait erat dengan perayaan panen, rasa syukur, dan persiapan menghadapi musim dingin."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/easter.tsx:64
msgid "Across many cultures, older symbols of rebirth — such as eggs, blossoms, and new growth — became woven into the celebration."
msgstr "Di banyak budaya, simbol-simbol kelahiran kembali yang lebih tua — seperti telur, bunga, dan tunas baru — terjalin ke dalam perayaan."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/total-lunar-eclipse.tsx:58
msgid "Across many cultures, the deep red colour of the eclipsed Moon inspired myths and the name “Blood Moon”."
msgstr "Di banyak budaya, warna merah tua Bulan yang sedang mengalami gerhana menginspirasi mitos dan sebutan “Bulan Darah”."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/winter-solstice.tsx:100
msgid "Across many cultures, traditions such as Yule and Saturnalia developed around this moment, gathering warmth, light, and community during the darkest part of the year in the regions where they first formed."
msgstr "Di banyak budaya, tradisi seperti Yule dan Saturnalia berkembang di sekitar momen ini, mengumpulkan kehangatan, cahaya, dan kebersamaan pada bagian tergelap tahun di wilayah tempat tradisi itu pertama kali terbentuk."

#: src/hooks/seasonal-events/spring-equinox.tsx:109
#~ msgid "Across the world, daylight begins to shift in new patterns as buds rise and the atmosphere carries the scent of change."
#~ msgstr "Di seluruh dunia, siang hari mulai bergeser dalam pola baru saat kuncup bermunculan dan udara membawa aroma perubahan."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/eid-al-adha.tsx:75
msgid "Acts of charity, the sharing of food, and care for family, neighbours, and those in need form the heart of the celebration."
msgstr "Tindakan amal, berbagi makanan, serta kepedulian pada keluarga, tetangga, dan mereka yang membutuhkan menjadi inti perayaan."

