#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/lunar-new-year.tsx:83
msgid "Traditional stories of the monster Nian are said to have inspired the use of loud sounds, firecrackers, and the colour red as symbols of protection and good fortune."
msgstr "Kisah tradisional tentang monster Nian konon menginspirasi penggunaan suara keras, petasan, dan warna merah sebagai simbol perlindungan dan keberuntungan."

